channel.title: Well..Looks like im gonna start modeling after all
channel.description:
After My first 3, I tried harder..this is what i got outta that.
Bloodchain Spear: [IMG]http://i372.photobucket.com/albums/oo163/Seerofdeath_derp/st00f-4.jpg[/img]
Spear Head: [IMG]http://i372.photobucket.com/albums/oo163/Seerofdeath_derp/st00fish2.jpg[/img] [IMG]http://i372.photobucket.com/albums/oo163/Seerofdeath_derp/st00fish.jpg[/img]
Chain Area: [IMG]http://i372.photobucket.com/albums/oo163/Seerofdeath_derp/st00fing2.jpg[/img] [IMG]http://i372.photobucket.com/albums/oo163/Seerofdeath_derp/st00fing.jpg[/img]
This is my best model so far ;)
To think, this started out as a sword. I was making a blade for a sword..then i looked at the blade for a little and thought, "wow that'd make a cool spear head if I change it up." Well, I hope you enjoyed it. ;)[br][br][size=1]Posted on: July 18, 2009, 08:01:15 pm[/size][hr]5th Try, getting beter! :eek:
I just call them Jet Wings...was gonna be like a glave of some kind..looked more like wings in the end..so i added the "jet" part in the hole. [IMG]http://i372.photobucket.com/albums/oo163/Seerofdeath_derp/jetwings.jpg[/img]
If you look in the middle, u'll see the handle i never removed =x [IMG]http://i372.photobucket.com/albums/oo163/Seerofdeath_derp/jetwings2.jpg[/img] The only prims are, the handle and "jet" part.
Its not flat btw..err ill post a side view...even if it's crooked..woot un1337 modeling skillz!
